igher efficiency. The proposed method can rapidly and simultaneously\ngenerate sCT with correct CT numbers and propagate contours from pCT to CBCT\nfor online ART re-planning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 02:03:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-02"}
