o the yield point. A comparison with the soft-sphere (SS) FCC\ncrystal reveals the similarities in the yielding behavior of both systems.\nNonetheless, diffusion of particles influences certain features, such as a less\nprominent increase in the local bond order parameters and local angles close to\nthe yield point.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 12:13:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-02"}
