\nknown that the spectrum comprises a continuous segment. We discuss the relation\nof our work with the general ground state problem and the question of\nconfinement in models with strong interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 14:59:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Apr 2021 19:44:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-16"}
