s investigated\nusing the surface redshift against the shell thickness and maximizing the\nentropy of the shell within the framework of Rastall gravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 07:26:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-14"}
